@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nrtgij(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(v0)
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.48 / v1 + 0.98)) * v1)
    v1 = 0.92
    v0 = ((0.79 - (tmp + 0.57 * v1 + 0.92)) * ((v2 + 0.12 - v1 + 0.39) - tmp))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.00)) / (tmp + wp.exp(tmp + 0.43)))
    data[tid] = v0
